  "message": "test(conformance): expand shape_stride_cases 36\u219247 with large shape/transpose coverage\n\nAdd 11 test cases for remaining SCE gaps:\n- Large shapes (65536\u00b2, 256\u2074, 1G elements) for overflow checks\n- 5D/6D transpose permutations (reverse, shuffle, cyclic)\n- Non-contiguous strided views\n- Large item size (complex128) stride calculations\n\nCoverage now includes full multi-axis transpose beyond 4D.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
